beartest.configurations.markdownDescription:
Test configurations that define both which files to discover and how to run them.

Each configuration matches files by pattern and specifies the runtime to use. Files are matched against patterns in order, using the first match.

**Simple project example:**
```json
[
  {
    "pattern": "**/*.test.*",
    "command": "node"
  }
]
```

**Monorepo example:**
```json
[
  {
    "pattern": "packages/frontend/**/*.test.ts",
    "command": "tsx",
    "runtimeArgs": ["--loader", "tsx"]
  },
  {
    "pattern": "packages/backend/**/*.test.js",
    "command": "node",
    "runtimeArgs": ["--require", "./test-setup.js"]
  }
]
```
